summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2676, for the improvement of the alley in blcok 7, Denny-Furhman's Addition to the City of Seattle, all in the City of Seattle, by grading and installing wooden curb on one side of said alley, under Ordinance No. 31535 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
